0fix%20his%20receding%20hairline%2C%20an%20issue%20that%20had%20long%20been%20on%20his%20mind.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20not%20for%20a%20high-paying%20job%20in%20finance%20%E2%80%94%20in%20private%20banking%20and%20now%20trading%20derivatives%20for%20an%20asset%20management%20firm%20%E2%80%94%20he%20said%20he%20wouldn't%20have%20taken%20the%20plunge%20on%20two%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhair-transplant-istanbul-turkey-personal-experience-business-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehair%20transplants%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20would%20look%20in%20the%20mirror%2C%20I%20would%20see%20my%20hair%20receding%2C%20and%20it%20would%20just%20take%20up%20some%20of%20my%20emotional%20and%20mental%20bandwidth%2C%26quot%3B%20John%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20spending%20%2418%2C600%20on%20his%20first%20procedure%20at%2025%2C%20he%20decided%20on%20another%20transplant%20four%20years%20later.%20He%20traveled%20to%20Turkey%20to%20cut%20the%20cost%2C%20spending%20%243%2C250%20in%20cash%2C%20which%20included%20airport%20transfers%2C%20a%20three-night%20stay%20with%20breakfast%20in%20a%20five-star%20hotel%2C%20the%20hair%20transplant%2C%20and%20postoperative%20care.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20nerves%20kicked%20in%20when%20he%20arrived%20and%20realized%20the%2010-%20to%2012-hour%20surgery%20would%20take%20place%20at%20a%20practice%20that%20wasn't%20as%20clean%2C%20welcoming%2C%20or%20professional%20as%20the%20one%20back%20in%20DC.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20the%20toll%20of%20worrying%20about%20other%20people's%20perceptions%20of%20him%20made%20it%20a%20gamble%20worth%20taking.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20previous%20role%20in%20private%20banking%2C%20John%20worked%20in%20sales%20with%20high-net-worth%20individuals%20and%20knew%20that%20the%20way%20he%20presented%20himself%20in%20meetings%20and%20pitches%20was%20%26quot%3Bincredibly%20important.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20his%20transplants%2C%20he%20said%20he%20felt%20more%20confident%20and%20spent%20less%20time%20questioning%20how%20clients%20and%20coworkers%20perceived%20him.%20Instead%2C%20he%20used%20that%20time%20to%20focus%20more%20on%20his%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNot%20thinking%20about%2C%20'Oh%2C%20do%20they%20notice%20my%20hair%20thinning%3F'%20or%20'Do%20they%20notice%20my%20receding%20hairline%3F'%20really%20allowed%20me%20to%20free%20up%20my%20mental%20space%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJohn%20isn't%20alone%20in%20making%20this%20type%20of%20investment%20in%20his%20career.%20Business%20Insider%20spoke%20to%20four%20men%20in%20the%20corporate%20world%20who%20are%20willing%20to%20spend%20a%20lot%20to%20look%20good%20for%20their%20jobs%2C%20investing%20in%20services%20from%20plastic%20surgery%20to%20hair-loss%20treatments%20and%20time-consuming%20self-care%20routines%20to%20gain%20a%20competitive%20edge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeople%20identified%20by%20only%20a%20first%20name%20were%20given%20pseudonyms%20because%20they%20feared%20career-related%20repercussions.%20Their%20identities%20are%20known%20to%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2259b57871-e32e-4738-bc85-a0020dbf4c8a%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20'Brotox'%20boost%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20five%20years%2C%20it's%20become%20less%20taboo%20for%20men%20to%20discuss%20their%20desire%20to%20undergo%20some%20type%20of%20rejuvenation%2C%20Dr.%20Daniel%20Maman%2C%20a%20plastic%20surgeon%20with%20a%20practice%20on%20Park%20Avenue%20in%20New%20York%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTen%20years%20ago%2C%20it%20was%20just%20a%20topic%20that%20wasn't%20discussed%20amongst%20men%2C%26quot%3B%20Maman%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20did%20have%20some%20men%20in%20the%20practice%2C%20but%20it%20was%20usually%20quite%20secretive%2C%20discreet.%20They%20were%20very%20nervous%20about%20coming%20in%2C%20nervous%20about%20seeing%20others.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20he%20said%2C%20some%20men%20view%20getting%20work%20done%20as%20basic%20maintenance%20%E2%80%94%20just%20like%20%26quot%3Bgetting%20a%20haircut.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%202023%20survey%20from%20the%20American%20Society%20of%20Plastic%20Surgeons%20found%20that%20the%20number%20of%20men%20getting%20cosmetic%20procedures%20in%20the%20US%20increased%20by%208%25%20from%202022%20to%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMaman%2C%20who's%2046%20and%20started%20getting%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finfluencers-botched-botox-job-leaves-one-of-her-eyes-drooping-2021-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBotox%3C%2Fa%3E%20two%20years%20ago%2C%20said%20men%20in%20fields%20like%20finance%2C%20business%2C%20and%20law%20start%20coming%20in%20their%20mid-40s%20when%20they%20see%20signs%20of%20aging.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20when%20Dan%2C%20a%2045-year-old%20corporate%20lawyer%20from%20New%20York%2C%20first%20got%20Botox.%20He's%20gotten%20the%20procedure%20twice%20%E2%80%94%20once%20at%2040%2C%20then%20at%2044%20%E2%80%94%20with%20each%20round%20costing%20about%20%241%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20want%20to%20keep%20a%20groomed%20and%20youthful%20appearance%2C%20but%20I%20also%20don't%20mind%20showing%20my%20age%20because%2C%20again%2C%20that%20comes%20with%20experience%20and%20maturity%20and%20authority%2C%26quot%3B%20Dan%20said.%20%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20little%20bit%20of%20tension%20between%20the%20two%2C%20and%20the%20sweet%20spot%20is%20balancing%20both.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMaman%20said%20it's%20also%20very%20common%20for%20men%20in%20high-status%20fields%20to%20want%20to%20look%20fresher%20and%20avoid%20looking%20tired.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYour%20appearance%20is%20oftentimes%2C%20for%20better%20or%20worse%2C%20an%20indication%20of%20the%20way%20you%20feel%20mentally%20as%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20Maman%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20take%20care%20of%20your%20skin%20and%20dress%20well%2C%20people%20may%20be%20more%20likely%20to%20perceive%20you%20as%20someone%20who%20has%20their%20life%20together%2C%20he%20said%2C%20which%20benefits%20you%20professionally%20%E2%80%94%20selling%20a%20product%20or%20getting%20people%20to%20follow%20you%20as%20a%20manager%20can%20be%20easier%20if%20you%20look%20fresh%20and%20polished.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225665%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Syrninge%20with%20liquid%20coming%20out%20of%20the%20tip%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6741fd34fa0140cdd5651630%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223776%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBotox%20is%20considered%20a%20minimally%20invasive%20procedure.%3Cp%3EAnna%20Efetova%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20been%20a%20general%20shift%20toward%20minimally%20invasive%20procedures%20across%20generations.%20The%20trend%20reflects%20%26quot%3Ba%20societal%20move%20toward%20treatments%20that%20provide%20effective%20yet%20less-intensive%20solutions%2C%20appealing%20to%20patients%20seeking%20quick%20recovery%20times%20and%20lower%20risks%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20ASPS%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.plasticsurgery.org%2Fdocuments%2Fnews%2Fstatistics%2F2023%2Fplastic-surgery-statistics-report-2023.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EASPS%20survey%3C%2Fa%3E%20found%20that%20Botox%20procedures%20increased%205.55%25%20among%20male%20patients%20from%202022%20to%202023%2C%20while%20minimally%20invasive%20treatments%20%E2%80%94%20which%20include%20Botox%20and%20procedures%20such%20as%20fillers%2C%20chemical%20peels%2C%20and%20laser%20hair%20removal%20%E2%80%94%20increased%207%25%20for%20both%20men%20and%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBotox%20is%20popular%20among%20men%20who%20have%20concerns%20about%20looking%20tired%20or%20sad%2C%20in%20part%20due%20to%20frown%20lines%2C%20Dr.%20Josef%20Hadeed%2C%20a%20plastic%20surgeon%20with%20practices%20in%20Miami%20and%20Beverly%20Hills%2C%20said.%20He%20said%20men%20make%20up%20around%2010%25%20to%2015%25%20of%20his%20clientele%20and%20about%20half%20of%20those%20men%20are%20corporate%20professionals%20who%20%26quot%3Bwant%20to%20look%20good%20in%20the%20workplace.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHadeed%20said%20some%20of%20his%20clients%20told%20him%20they%20feel%20they%20could%20be%20passed%20over%20for%20opportunities%20if%20they%20don't%20look%20as%20good%20as%20younger%20colleagues%20%E2%80%94%20and%20believe%20they%20might%20gain%20a%20competitive%20edge%20by%20having%20work%20done.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20John%20is%20only%2029%2C%20he%20is%20already%20thinking%20about%20Botox%20and%20isn't%20ruling%20it%20out%20in%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20feel%20like%20I%20look%20older%20than%20I%20am%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20When%20he%20was%20in%20his%20early%2020s%2C%20he'd%20take%20it%20as%20a%20compliment%20when%20he%20was%20told%20he%20looked%20like%20he%20was%20in%20his%2030s.%20As%20he%20gets%20closer%20to%20his%2030s%2C%20however%2C%20he's%20thinking%20about%20what%20he'll%20do%20to%20maintain%20a%20more%20youthful%20appearance%20down%20the%20road.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20now%2C%20John%20is%20taking%20a%20less%20invasive%20approach.%20He%20said%20he%20spends%20around%20%241%2C050%20each%20quarter%20on%20fitness%20memberships%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F4-new-hair-loss-treatments-discovered-this-year-2022-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehair-loss-prevention%20medication%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20supplements.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22093d7df4-e6e1-4702-bec6-3c9771976d69%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EFinding%20a%20competitive%20edge%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20Darrell%20Spencer%20entered%20the%20spotlight%20as%20a%20senior%20leader%20launching%20two%20companies%20%E2%80%94%20the%20skincare%20brand%20Crowned%20Skin%20and%20the%20hair-care%20brand%20Kings%20Crowning%20%E2%80%94%20he%20also%20started%20investing%20more%20in%20his%20appearance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%2028-year-old%20spends%20around%20%243%2C623%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ea%20