Survey%20found.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETim%20Peters%2C%20a%2043-year-old%20chief%20marketing%20officer%2C%20has%20noticed%20that%20social%20media%20is%20opening%20the%20door%20for%20more%20conversations%20about%20self-care%20regimens%20among%20his%20close%20circle%20of%20male%20friends%20compared%20to%2010%20years%20ago.%20He%20spends%20about%20%241%2C464%20a%20quarter%20on%20fitness%2C%20supplements%2C%20skincare%2C%20and%20personal%20upkeep.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20definitely%20feel%20more%20comfortable%20asking%20friends%2C%20'Hey%2C%20are%20you%20taking%20certain%20supplements%2C%20or%20what%20are%20you%20doing%3F'%26quot%3B%20Peters%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22814070bd-b85c-42ed-a3ca-0e91baf9c820%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWall%20Street's%20best-kept%20secret%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20men%20still%20remain%20uncomfortable%20discussing%20more%20extensive%20procedures%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20with%20people%20they%20work%20with.%20After%20all%2C%20Maman%20said%20remote%20work%20and%20camera-off%20meetings%20could%20make%20it%20easier%20for%20people%20to%20get%20procedures%20and%20recover%20from%20them%2C%20with%20colleagues%20none%20the%20wiser.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERemote%20work%20was%20partly%20why%20John%20took%20the%20leap%20on%20his%20first%20hair%20procedure%20because%20he%20could%20%26quot%3Bafford%20to%20look%20like%20Frankenstein%20for%20a%20few%20weeks%26quot%3B%20if%20he%20kept%20his%20camera%20off%20in%20meetings%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20was%20a%20time%20period%20where%20I%20wasn't%20the%20prettiest%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20was%20back%20in%20the%20office%20on%20day%2010%20following%20the%20second%20procedure%20when%20he%20still%20had%20some%20scabs%20and%20facial%20swelling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20men%20just%20don't%20talk%20about%20the%20work%20they%20get%20done%2C%20said%20Dr.%20Catherine%20Chang%2C%20a%20plastic%20surgeon%20and%20the%20founder%20of%20Priv%C3%A9%20Beverly%20Hills.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20really%20hard%20for%20me%20to%20get%20men%20to%20let%20me%20share%20their%20photos%2C%20which%20is%20why%20I%20don't%20have%20a%20ton%2C%20but%20they're%20coming%20in%20the%20door%2C%20which%20I%20think%20is%20the%20first%20step%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20before-and-after%20pictures%20of%20procedures%20that%20she%20provides%20as%20examples%20for%20potential%20clients.%20She%20told%20BI%20that%20men%20make%20up%20around%2030%25%20of%20her%20clientele.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMen%20may%20confide%20in%20professionals%20like%20Chang%20or%20Roy%20Cohen%2C%20the%20career%20coach%2C%20about%20their%20insecurities%20and%20anxieties%20around%20their%20appearance%20and%20possible%20procedures%20but%20may%20not%20share%20them%20openly%20with%20colleagues%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20in%20competitive%20fields%20where%20having%20an%20edge%20is%20important.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20secret%20everyone%20knows%20about%2C%26quot%3B%20Cohen%20said.%20%26quot%3BWall%20Street%20is%20very%20competitive%2C%20so%20why%20would%20I%20share%20that%20information%20with%20somebody%20who%20could%20be%20competing%20with%20me%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20swagger%20that%20often%20defines%20how%20people%20want%20to%20appear%20at%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20%26quot%3BYou%20can't%20have%20swagger%20when%20people%20think%20you've%20been%20artificially%20enhanced.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmen-corporate-america-expensive-beauty-routines-spending-thousands-2024-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733317681000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F671961b801ea6d83dee3a07c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmen-corporate-america-expensive-beauty-routines-spending-thousands-2024-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Many%20men%20in%20corp