3EThe%20platform%20recently%20went%20viral%20after%20it%20launched%20its%20%26quot%3Bdeep%20dive%2C%26quot%3B%20podcast-like%20discussion%20hosted%20by%20two%20conversational%20AI%20hosts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20Spotify%20feature%20enlists%20the%20voices%20of%20the%20same%20two%20AI%20hosts%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-notebooklm-audio-overviews-ai-podcast-tool-2024-01%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENotebookLM's%20Audio%20Overview%20feature%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20discuss%20users'%20favorite%20artists%2C%20songs%2C%20and%20genres%20from%20the%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20the%20first%20of%20its%20kind%20integration%2C%20and%20it%20demonstrates%20the%20potential%20of%20AI%20to%20enhance%20personalized%20experiences%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Steven%20Johnson%2C%20Head%20of%20Editorial%20at%20Google%20Labs%2C%20in%20a%20press%20event%20for%20the%20launch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Wrapped%20AI%20podcast%20on%20Spotify%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F674f8a3a7929f317fb4fd698%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUsers%20can%20listen%20to%20an%20AI%20podcast%20about%20their%20music%20choices%20of%20the%20year.%3Cp%3ESpotify%2FGoogle%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20podcast%20is%20unique%20to%20each%20user%2C%20reflecting%20their%20personal%20listening%20habits%20from%20the%20year%2C%20Johnson%20said.%20He%20also%20said%20it%20demonstrates%20the%20potential%20of%20AI%20to%20enhance%20these%20personalized%20experiences%20%E2%80%94%20and%20raised%20the%20point%20that%20most%20people%20don't%20have%20on-demand%20hosts%20to%20sit%20around%20and%20talk%20about%20their%20music%20choices%20from%20the%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20wonderful%2C%20robust%20market%20for%20podcasts%20on%20many%20topics%2C%26quot%3B%20Johnson%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20having%20customized%20top%20podcasts%20for%20millions%20of%20individual%20people%20based%20on%20their%20specific%20listening%20habits%20for%20the%20year%2C%20is%20just%20not%20something%20that%20you%20can%20do%20with%20actual%20humans.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJohnson%20said%20NotebookLM%20has%20been%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20customizable%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20told%20BI%20that%20in%20the%20initial%20wave%20of%20AI%2C%20people%20conversed%20with%20models%20that%20knew%20a%20lot%20about%20the%20world%2C%20but%20nothing%20about%20the%20user%20asking%20the%20questions.%20When%20a%20reliable%20model%20is%20able%20to%20bring%20out%20these%20insights%20and%20make%20it%20interesting%2C%20that's%20when%20you%20see%20a%20change%20in%20the%20way%20computers%20can%20work%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20the%20AI%20podcast%20feature%20on%20Spotify%20is%20only%20available%20with%20Wrapped.%20However%2C%20you%20can%20customize%20your%20own%20podcasts%20on%20NotebookLM's%20platform.%20Johnson%20also%20said%20the%20team%20is%20looking%20forward%20to%20%26quot%3Ba%20lot%20of%20different%20partnerships%2C%26quot%3B%20both%20in%20audio%20and%20text.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJust%20over%20a%20month%20after%20Google's%20NotebookLM%20Audio%20Overview%20tool%20went%20viral%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-notebooklm-ai-podcast-tool-customize-feature-update-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENotebookLM%20introduced%20a%20%26quot%3BCustomize%26quot%3B%20button%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20enabling%20users%20to%20guide%20the%20AI%20conversation.%20Its%20partnership%20with%20Spotify%20takes%20that%20customization%20a%20step%20further.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle%20has%20implemented%20more%20personalized%20features%20across%20several%20of%20its%20platforms%2C%20including%20Google%20Shopping.%20Google%20Shopping%20now%20provides%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-shopping-ai-features-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epers