first-transgender-lawyer-to-argue-before-us-supreme-court%2Farticleshow%2F115963583.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fwho-is-chase-strangio-first-transgender-lawyer-to-argue-before-us-supreme-court%2Famp_articleshow%2F115963583.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fwho-is-chase-strangio-first-transgender-lawyer-to-argue-before-us-supreme-court%2Famp_articleshow%2F115963583.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Suicide%20Deaths%20In%20Paramilitary%20Forces%20Rise%2C%20100-Day%20Leave%20Policy%20A%20Relief%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ELong%20hours%20of%20duty%20and%20sleep%20deprivation%20are%20not%20only%20making%20jawans%20posted%20with%20the%20Central%20Armed%20Police%20Forces%20(CAPF)%20to%20die%20by%20suicide%2C%20but%20also%20take%20voluntary%20retirement%20before%20they%20complete%20their%20service.%20The%20Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs%20(MHA)%20in%20data%20shared%20with%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20said%20730%20jawans%20have%20died%20by%20suicide%2C%20and%20over%2055%2C000%20either%20resigned%20or%20took%20voluntary%20retirement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMainly%2C%20death%20by%20suicide%20among%20jawans%20is%20due%20to%20personal%20reasons.%20The%20task%20force%20that%20studied%20reasons%20for%20increase%20in%20suicide%20among%20CAPF%20personnel%20said%20more%20than%2080%20per%20cent%20of%20those%20who%20died%20by%20suicide%20were%20reported%20after%20they%20returned%20home%20from%20leave.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMainly%20reasons%20include%20the%20death%20of%20a%20spouse%20or%20family%20member%2C%20marital%20discord%20or%20divorce%2C%20financial%20difficulties%2C%20and%20inadequate%20education%20opportunities%20for%20children%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20tackle%20this%2C%20the%20MHA%20said%20it%20has%20been%20ensuring%20more%20and%20more%20personnel%20get%20time%20to%20spend%20with%20their%20families.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20MHA%20in%20the%20data%20shared%20with%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20said%2042%2C797%20jawans%20used%20this%20leave%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20year%20till%20October%2C%206%2C302%20personnel%20spent%20100%20days%20with%20their%20family%2C%26quot%3B%20Minister%20of%20State%20for%20Home%20Nityanand%20Rai%20told%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha.%20The%20figure%20was%208%2C636%20in%202023%2C%20and%207%2C864%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20MHA%20task%20force%20has%20been%20asked%20to%20take%20steps%20for%20remedial%20measures%20to%20prevent%20suicide%20and%20fratricide%20in%20the%20CAPFs%20and%20the%20Assam%20Rifles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERegular%20interaction%20of%20officers%20with%20troops%20to%20find%20out%20and%20redress%20their%20grievances.%20Ensuring%20adequate%20rest%20and%20relief%20by%20regulating%20duty%20hours.%20Improving%20living%20conditions%20for%20troops%2C%20and%20providing%20adequate%20recreations%20are%20some%20of%20the%20suggestions%20the%20MHA%20has%20recommended.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20highlights%20suicide%20triggers%20can%20stem%20from%20both%20family%20and%20duty-related%20issues%2C%20with%20smoother%20experiences%20on%20either%20front%20significantly%20reducing%20stress%20among%20jawans.%20It%20noted%20a%20lower%20incidence%20of%20suicide%20attempts%20among%20female%20personnel%20compared%20to%20males%2C%20attributing%20male%20reluctance%20in%20sharing%20problems%20for%20fear%20of%20ridicule%20from%20peers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20report%20flagged%20professional%20challenges%20as%20potential%20triggers%2C%20a%20majority%20of%20personnel%20reported%20it%20is%20not%20the%20only%20cause%20of%20deaths%20by%20suicide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20has%20suggested%20key%20recommendations%20and%20the%20way%20forward%20in%20different%20forces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20different%20forces%2C%20so%20far%2C%20the%20efforts%20made%20towards%20stress%20management%20are%20haphazard%2C%20sporadic%20and%20generally%20not%20carried%20to%20their%20logical%20conclusions%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20task%20force%20suggested%20a%20transparent%20leave%20management%20system%2C%20with%20leaves%20reserved%20at%20each%20rank%20to%20enable%20liberal%20grant%20of%20leave.%20It%20said%20a%20transparent%20transfer%20policy%20is%20also%20needed.%20Inadequate%20promotional%20avenues%20in%20the%20service%20demoralise%20personnel%2C%20and%20so%20the%20promotion%20policy%20may%20be%20reviewed%20to%20boost%20morale%20of%20jawans%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ctable%3E%3Cthead%3E%3Ctr%3E%3Cth%20colspan%3D%5C%222%5C%22%3EHelplines%3C%2Fth%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%3C%2Fthead%3E%3Ctbody%3E%3Ctr%3E%3Ctd%3EVandrevala%20Foundation%20for%20Mental%20Health%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22tel%3A%2B919999666555%5C%22%3E9999666555%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Ahelp%40vandrevalafoundation.com%5C%22%3Ehelp%40vandrevalafoundation.com%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3C%2Ftd%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%3Ctr%3E%3Ctd%3ETISS%20iCall%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22tel%3A%2B912225521111%5C%22%3E022-25521111%3C%2Fa%3E%20(Monday-Saturday%3A%208%20am%20to%2010%20pm)%3C%2Ftd%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%20%3Ctr%3E%3Ctd%20colspan%3D%5C%222%5C%22%3E(If%20you%20need%20support%20or%20know%20someone%20who%20does%2C%20please%20reach%20out%20to%20your%20nearest%20mental%20health%20specialist.)%3C%2Ftd%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%3C%2Ftbody%3E%3C%2Ftable%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733312580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2F9uu4hta8_indian-border-bsf_625x300_15_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsuicide-deaths-in-paramilitary-forces-rise-100-day-leave-policy-a-relief-home-ministry-to-rajya-sabha-7170955%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Long%20hours%20of%20duty%20and%20sleep%20deprivation%20are%20not%20only%20making%20jawans%20posted%20with%20the%20Central%20Armed%20Police%20Forces%20(CAPF)%20to%20