C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Fadnavis%2C%20seated%20next%20to%20Mr%20Shinde%20and%20Mr%20Pawar%20during%20a%20press%20meet%20after%20their%20Raj%20Bhavan%20visit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20days%20of%20political%20posturing%20by%20Sena%20leaders%20stressing%20that%20Mr%20Shinde's%20contribution%20to%20the%20poll%20win%20must%20not%20be%20overlooked%2C%20Mr%20Fadnavis%20said%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20post%20was%20just%20a%20%26quot%3Btechnical%20understanding%26quot%3B%20between%20the%20allies.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20taken%20decisions%20together%20and%20this%20will%20continue.%20We%20will%20work%20together%20for%20Maharashtra.%20A%20decision%20on%20other%20ministers%20will%20be%20taken%20in%20subsequent%20meetings.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20the%20media%2C%20Mr%20Pawar%20said%20the%20Mahayuti%20will%20run%20a%20stable%20government%20for%20five%20years%20and%20no%20MLA%20will%20flee%20his%2Fher%20party.%20%26quot%3BWe%20will%20work%20together%20for%20Maharashtra's%20development.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Shinde%20said%20Mr%20Fadnavis%20had%20recommended%20him%20for%20Chief%20Minister%20two-and-a-half%20years%20back.%20%26quot%3BThis%20time%2C%20I%20recommended%20his%20name.%26quot%3B%20The%20Sena%20chief%20evaded%20a%20question%20on%20whether%20he%20would%20take%20oath%20as%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20tomorrow.%20%26quot%3BYou%20will%20know%20tomorrow%20evening.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAjit%20Pawar%20quipped%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20will%20take%20the%20oath.%20Shinde%20ji%20will%20inform%20by%20the%20evening.%26quot%3B%20The%20exchange%20suggested%20that%20more%20drama%20could%20be%20in%20the%20offing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Sena%20chief%20became%20Chief%20Minister%20in%202022%20after%20a%20rebellion%20he%20led%20split%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20and%20toppled%20the%20Uddhav%20Thackeray-led%20government%20of%20undivided%20Sena%2C%20Congress%20and%20NCP.%20Back%20then%2C%20despite%20holding%20more%20numerical%20strength%20in%20the%20House%2C%20t