0made%20of%20dreams.%20For%20one%20family%20in%20Noida%2C%20a%20string%20of%20tragedies%20turned%20the%20search%20for%20a%20home%20into%20a%20long%20wait%20for%20justice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202011%2C%20Rashmi%20Bhatnagar%20and%20Sanjeev%20Kumar%20Bhatnagar%20bought%20a%20flat%20at%20Jaypee%20Kube%20in%20Noida%20Sector%20128%20for%20nearly%20Rs%2039%20lakh.%20Over%20the%20next%20three%20years%2C%20Mr%20Bhatnagar%2C%20who%20was%20then%20working%20as%20a%20retired%20consultant%2C%20made%20payments%20totalling%20over%20Rs%2020%20lakh%20of%20the%20Rs%2027%20lakh%20demanded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20husband%20handled%20all%20the%20transactions.%20I%20had%20limited%20understanding%20of%20such%20matters%20so%20I%20did%20not%20really%20get%20into%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Bhatnagar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2F2bdmb90g_jaypee-kube_625x300_04_December_24.jpeg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20over%2070%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20payment%20done%2C%20the%20Bhatnagars%20were%20close%20to%20their%20dream%20home.%20But%20life%20had%20other%20plans.%20In%202015%2C%20Mr%20Bhatnagar%20suffered%20a%20silent%20heart%20attack.%20He%20had%20been%20suffering%20from%20severe%20diabetes%20and%20the%20heart%20attack%2C%20and%20the%20damage%20it%20caused%20went%20unnoticed.%20In%202017%2C%20just%20three%20weeks%20after%20his%20mother's%20death%2C%20Mr%20Bhatnagar%20died%20of%20a%20cardiac%20arrest.%20The%20back-to-back%20losses%20crippled%20the%20family%20emotionally%2C%20but%20another%20tragedy%20was%20waiting%20in%20the%20wings.%20Soon%20after%20Mr%20Bhatnagar's%20death%2C%20his%20daughter%20went%20through%20a%20difficult%20separation%20and%20returned%20to%20her%20parents'%20home%20with%20a%20little%20daughter.%20Within%20a%20few%20months%2C%20the%20Bhatnagars'%20world%20had%20come%20crashing%20down.%20Outside%20the%20Bhatnagar%20home%2C%20another%20story%20was%20unfolding.%20Jaypee%20Infratech%20had%20entered%20insolvency%2C%20throwing%20thousands%20of%20homebuyers%20into%20an%20abyss%20of%20uncertainty.%20But%20the%20Bhatnagars%2C%20struggling%20to%20cope%20with%20personal%20tragedies%2C%20could%20not%20keep%20track.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20completely%20lost%20and%20consumed%20by%20these%20personal%20tragedies.%20I%20could%20not%20focus%20on%20the%20status%20of%20our%20flat%20or%20the%20developments%20in%20the%20insolvency%20case.%20To%20make%20matters%20worse%2C%20communications%20from%20Jaypee%20Infratech%20went%20to%20my%20late%20husband's%20inbox%2C%26quot%3B%20Mrs%20Bhatnagar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20much%20later%20that%20the%20couple's%20son%20went%20through%20the%20flat's%20documents%20and%20the%20family%20realised%20that%20they%20had%20missed%20the%20deadlines%20to%20claim%20their%20dream%20home.%20The%20family%20wrote%20multiple%20emails%20to%20Jaypee%20and%20Surkasha%20Group%2C%20which%20had%20acquired%20the%20debt-ridden%20real%20estate%20firm%2C%20but%20got%20no%20response.%20Mrs%20Bhatnagar%20has%20now%20approached%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20requesting%20its%20help%20in%20getting%20her%20flat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20delay%20in%20addressing%20the%20Jaypee%20flat%20issue%20was%20due%20to%20an%20overwhelming%20combination%20of%20grief%2C%20loss%2C%20and%20lack%20of%20access%20to%20essential%20information.%20My%20late%20husband%20invested%20nearly%20our%20life%20savings%20into%20this%20flat%20that%20has%20now%20become%20entangled%20in%20bureaucratic%20challenges%20beyond%20my%20control%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20In%20November%2C%20a%20bench%20led%20by%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%2C%20Sanjiv%20Khanna%2C%20issued%20a%20notice%20in%20her%20petition%20filed%20through%20Prateek%20Mishra%2C%20Advocate-on-Record%2C%20and%20has%20agreed%20to%20hear%20her%20pleas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Bhatnagar%20says%20she%20does%20not%20want%20a%20refund%20and%20is%20fighting%20to%20get%20the%20house.%20%26quot%3BThis%20house%20is%20so%20much%20more%20than%20just%20a%20property%20to%20me.%20It's%20a%20reminder%20of%20my%20late%20husband%2C%20Sanjeev%2C%20and%20all%20the%20dreams%20we%20built%20together.%20It%20holds%20not%20just%20our%20financial%20investment%2C%20but%20the%20emotional%20threads%20of%20a%20life%20we%20had%20planned%20as%20a%20family.%20Losing%20him%20was%20devastating%2C%20and%20now%20the%20thought%20of%20losing%20this%20home%20feels%20like%20losing%20a%20part%20of%20him%20all%20over%20again.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20not%20seeking%20a%20refund%3B%20I%20am%20fighting%20to%20have%20the%20house%2C%20which%20means%20so%20much%20to%20me%20and%20my%20family.%20I%20have%20immense%20faith%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20and%20have%20placed%20my%20hopes%20on%20the%20petition%20I%20have%20filed%20before%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Is%20Jaypee%20Insolvency%20Case%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20dreams%20of%20thousands%20of%20homebuyers%20took%20a%20massive%20blow%20when%20debt-ridden%20Jaypee%20Infratech%20entered%20insolvency%20proceedings%20in%202017.%20What%20started%20was%20a%20long-drawn%20process%20riddled%20with%20legal%20complications.%20After%20the%20Suraksha%20Realty%20group%20finally%20got%20regulatory%20clearances%20several%20years%20later%2C%20a%20large%20section%20of%20homemakers%20filed%20their%20claims.%20Many%2C%20however%2C%20were%20not%20informed%20of%20the%20developments%20and%20missed%20the%20deadline.%20They%20then%20had%20to%20approach%20the%20courts%20and%20seek%20their%20intervention.%20While%20the%20processes%20are%20nearing%20completion%2C%20many%20like%20Rashmi%20Bhatnagar%20are%20still%20waiting%20for%20their%20dream%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20number%20of%20homeowners%20who