nsider.com%2Finflation-october-cpi-consumer-price-index-federal-reserve-interest-rates-2024-11%5C%22%3Econsumer%20price%20index%20ticked%20up%20slightly%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%20a%20speech%20in%20Washington%2C%20D.C.%20on%20Monday%2C%20Fed%20Governor%20Christopher%20Waller%20addressed%20concerns%20that%20inflation%20could%20stagnate%20above%20the%20Fed's%202%25%20target%20and%20whether%20the%20Fed%20should%20consider%20pausing%20its%20rate%20cuts%20at%20its%20meeting%20later%20this%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBased%20on%20the%20economic%20data%20in%20hand%20today%20and%20forecasts%20that%20show%20that%20inflation%20will%20continue%20on%20its%20downward%20path%20to%202%25%20over%20the%20medium%20term%2C%20at%20present%20I%20lean%20toward%20supporting%20a%20cut%20to%20the%20policy%20rate%20at%20our%20December%20meeting%2C%26quot%3B%20Waller%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20that%20decision%20will%20depend%20on%20whether%20data%20that%20we%20will%20receive%20before%20then%20surprises%20to%20the%20upside%20and%20alters%20my%20forecast%20for%20the%20path%20of%20inflation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20Fed%20ends%20up%20holding%20rates%20steady%20at%20its%20next%20meeting%2C%20we%20could%20see%20mortgage%20rates%20tick%20up%20a%20bit.%20And%20if%20inflation%20remains%20stubborn%2C%20we%20might%20not%20see%20rates%20drop%20as%20much%20in%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Caside%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECheck%20your%20rate%20online%20and%20see%20how%20much%20house%20you%20can%20afford%20with%20Mortgage%20Research%20Center%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cstrong%3E.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Faside%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Current%20Mortgage%20Rates%5C%22%3ECurrent%20Mortgage%20Rates%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Current%20Refinance%20Rates%5C%22%3ECurrent%20Refinance%20Rates%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Ch3%3EMortgage%20Calculator%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EUse%20our%C2%A0%3Ca%20data-analytics-module%3D%5C%22body_link%5C%22%20data-analytics-post-depth%3D%5C%2240%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsid