leged%20long%20hours%2C%20early%20morning%20meetings%2C%20and%20exploitation%20of%20young%20workers.%20Palicha%20acknowledged%20the%20unusual%20meeting%20times%20due%20to%20his%20schedule%20and%20hiring%20practices%20but%20recommended%20work-life%20balance%20to%20competitors.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20TECH%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22South%20Korean%20Opposition%20Submits%20Motion%20To%20Impeach%20President%20Yoon%3A%2010%20Facts%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20opposition%20parties%20in%20South%20Korea%2C%20whose%20lawmakers%20tussled%20with%20security%20forces%20to%20vote%20down%20the%20controversial%20martial%20law%2C%20filed%20a%20motion%20on%20Wednesday%20to%20impeach%20President%20Yoon%20Suk%20Yeol.%20%26quot%3BWe've%20submitted%20an%20impeachment%20motion%20prepared%20urgently%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Kim%20Yong-min%20of%20the%20opposition%20Democratic%20Party%20(DP).%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ELawmakers%20are%20yet%20to%20decide%20when%20the%20impeachment%20motion%20will%20be%20put%20to%20a%20vote%2C%20but%20it%20could%20come%20as%20soon%20as%20Friday.%20South%20Korea's%20opposition%20controls%20the%20National%20Assembly.%20The%20opposition%20has%20threatened%20to%20impeach%20President%20Yoon%20if%20he%20does%20not%20resign%20voluntarily%2C%20following%20his%20ill-fated%20move%20to%20impose%20martial%20law.%20In%20case%20Mr%20Yoon%20quits%20or%20is%20removed%20from%20office%20then%2C%20the%20South%20Korean%20constitution%20mandates%20that%20Prime%20Minister%20Han%20Duck-soo%20steps%20in%20to%20perform%20presidential%20duties.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EEarlier%20the%20DP%20in%20a%20statement%20said%20it%20would%20file%20charges%20of%20%26quot%3Binsurrection%2C%26quot%3B%20against%20Yoon%2C%20his%20defence%20and%20interior%20ministers%20and%20%26quot%3Bkey%20military%20and%20police%20figures%20involved%2C%20such%20as%20the%20martial%20law%20commander%20and%20the%20police%20chief.%26quot%3B%20The%20National%20Assembly%20can%20impeach%20the%20president%20if%20more%20than%20two-thirds%20of%20lawmakers%20vote%20for%20it.%20A%20trial%20is%20then%20held%20by%20the%20constitutional%20court%2C%20which%20can%20confirm%20it%20with%20a%20vote%20by%20six%20of%20the%20nine%20justices.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20opposition%20in%20South%20Korea%20holds%20a%20large%20majority%20in%20the%20300-member%20parliament%20and%20needs%20only%20a%20handful%20of%20defections%20from%20the%20president's%20party%20to%20secure%20the%20two-thirds%20majority%20needed%20to%20pass%20the%20motion.%20Earlier%2C%20even%20the%20leader%20of%20Yoon's%20own%20ruling%20party%2C%20which%20controls%20108%20seats%20in%20the%20300-member%20legislature%2C%20described%20the%20attempt%20to%20bring%20the%20martial%20law%20as%20%26quot%3Btragic%26quot%3B%20while%20calling%20for%20those%20involved%20to%20be%20held%20accountable.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESouth%20Korean%20stocks%20sank%20on%20Wednesday%20while%20the%20currency%20won%20dipping%20multi-year%20lows%20only%20to%20rebound%20later%20after%20the%20shocking%20announcement%20on%20Tuesday%20night.%20The%20hours%20of%20martial%20rule%20in%20the%20country%20sent%20shivers%20through%20the%20trading%20floor%20in%20Seoul%2C%20with%20investors%20keeping%20a%20close%20eye%20on%20developments%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20Kospi%20index%20ended%20down%20more%20than%20one%20per%20cent%2C%20having%20shed%20as%20much%20as%202.3%20per%20cent%20at%20the%20open%2C%20as%20traders%20fretted%20over%20the%20impact%20of%20Yoon%20declaring%20the%20Asian%20country's%20first%20martial%20law%20in%20more%20than%20four%20decades.%20Analysts%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20upheaval%20comes%20as%20authorities%20steeled%20for%20the%20second%20US%20presidency%20of%20Donald%20Trump%20who%20has%20vowed%20to%20reignite%20his%20hardball%20trade%20policy.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20South%20Korean%20finance%20ministry%20and%20central%20bank%20looked%20to%20provide%20stability%20and%20reassure%20markets%20by%20promising%20to%20pour%20in%20money%20if%20needed%20to%20prop%20up%20volatile%20financial%20markets.%20%26quot%3BAs%20announced%20together%20with%20the%20government%2C%20it%20has%20been%20decided%20to%20temporarily%20supply%20sufficient%20liquidity%20until%20the%20financial%20and%20foreign%20exchange%20markets%20stabilise%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Bank%20of%20Korea%20said.%20It%20added%20that%20%26quot%3Bthe%20range%20of%20securities%20eligible%20for%20(repo)%20transactions%20and%20the%20target%20institutions%20will%20be%20expanded%26quot%3B.%20Deputy%20Prime%20Minister%20Choi%20Sang-mok%2C%20who%20also%20holds%20the%20economy%20portfolio%2C%20said%20financial%20authorities%20will%20keep%20international%20partners%20informed%20about%20developments.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESouth%20Koreans%20continued%20with%20their%20lives%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20with%20people%20going%20to%20offices%2C%20businesses%20and%20schools%20as%20usual.%20There%20were%20scarcely%20any%20visible%20signs%20in%20the%20capital%20Seoul%20that%20six%20hours%20of%20surprise%20martial%20law%20and%20high%20political%20drama%20overnight%20had%20spilled%20into%20everyday%20life.%20The%20city%20of%209%20million%20started%20the%20day%20normally%20with%20the%20usual%20morning%20rush%20hour%20in%20trains%20and%20on%20the%20streets.%20%26quot%3BAt%20first%2C%20I%20was%20scared%20and%20very%20confused.%20I%20kept%20thinking%2C%20'What%20is%20going%20on%3F%20Is%20this%20something%20that%20could%20actually%20happen%20in%20this%20era%3F'%20I%20couldn't%20sleep%20until%20the%20martial%20law%20was%20lifted%20because%20I%20was%20so%20frightened%2C%26quot%3B%20Seoul%20resident%20Gang%20He-Soo%2C%2050%2C%20told%20Reuters.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EPresident%20Yoon%20declared%20martial%20law%20in%20a%20live%20TV%20address%20at%20around%2010%3A30%20pm%20(13%3A30%20GMT)%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20only%20to%20reverse%20the%20decree%20after%20lawmakers%20defied%20police%20and%20special%20forces%20condoning%20the%20National%20Assembly%20to%20vote%2C%20forcing%20him%20to%20lift%20the%20order.%20The%20president's%20office%20said%20the%20declaration%20of%20martial%20law%20was%20done%20at%20night%20to%20%26quot%3Bminimize%20damage%20to%20the%20national%20economy%20and%20people's%20lives%26quot%3B.%20South%20Korean%20soldiers%2C%20equipped%20with%20rifles%2C%20body%20armour%20and%20night-vision%20equipment%2C%20were%20seen%20entering%20the%20parliament%20building%20in%20Seoul%20through%20smashed%20windows%2C%20while%20helicopters%20hovered%20in%20the%20night%20sky%20above%20the%20building.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESoon%20after%20the%20news%20broke%20of%20the%20martial%20law%20broke%2C%20thousands%20of%20protesters%20stepped%20out%20on%20the%20streets%2C%20asking%20for%20the%20decree's%20reversal%20and%20removal%20of%20the%20President.%20Flag-waving%20protesters%20kept%20vigil%20outside%20parliament%20braving%20freezing%20temperatures%20through%20the%20night%20in%20defiance%20of%20Mr%20Yoon's%20martial%20law%20order.%20Several%20senior%20aides%20working%20for%20Mr%20Yoon%20also%20offered%20Wednesday%20to%20resign%20en%20masse%20over%20the%20martial%20law%20declaration.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733305200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fob78bpk8_south-korea-martial-law-reuters_625x300_04_December_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fsouth-korean-opposition-submits-motion-to-impeach-president-yoon-10-facts-7169969%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20lawmakers%20of%20South%20Korea's%20opposition%20coalition%20on%20Wednesday%20moved%20a%20motion%20in%20the%20Asian%20country's%20Parliament%20to%20impeach%20President%20Yoon%20Suk%20Yeol%20after%20his%20shocking%20imposition%20of%20martial%20law%20that%20brought%20thousands%20of%20protesters%20to%20the%20streets.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22