mped%20on%20the%20western%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20town%20after%20four%20people%20were%20killed%20and%20several%20others%20injured%20in%20violent%20clashes%20with%20police%20during%20a%20court-ordered%20survey%20of%20the%20Shahi%20Jama%20Masjid.%20The%20Mughal-era%20mosque%20is%20at%20the%20centre%20of%20a%20legal%20battle%20after%20some%20petitions%20claimed%20it%20was%20built%20on%20the%20site%20of%20a%20Hindu%20temple.%20Local%20Samajwadi%20Party%20MP%20Zia%20Ur%20Rehman%2C%20Samajwadi%20Party%20MLA%20Mahmood's%20son%20Sohail%20Iqbal%20and%20over%20700%20unidentified%20people%20have%20been%20charged%20in%20the%20FIR%20filed%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20and%20administration%20have%20said%20they%20would%20not%20allow%20outsiders%20to%20visit%20the%20area%2C%20citing%20the%20law%20and%20order%20situation.%20The%20prohibitory%20orders%20have%20been%20extended%20to%20December%2031.%20Earlier%2C%20a%20delegation%20of%20Samajwadi%20Party%20MPs%20was%20stopped%20from%20entering%20the%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733304540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fhdbvnjng_rahul-gandhi_625x300_04_December_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frahul-gandhi-sambhal-visit-video-rahul-gandhi-asks-why-he-cant-go-to-sambhal-cop-says-law-order-7169862%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Stopped%20from%20visiting%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Sambhal%20to%20meet%20the%20families%20of%20those%20killed%20in%20the%20November%2024%20violence%2C%20Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20has%20said%20it%20was%20his%20right%20and%20duty%20as%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20to%20visit%20the%20town%20and%20speak%20to%20the%20families%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frahul-gandhi-sambhal-visit-video-rahul-gandhi-asks-why-he-cant-go-to-sambhal-cop-says-law-order-7169862%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Taming%20The%20Aussies%3A%20How%20India%20Is%20Staying%20On%20Top%20Down%20Under%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fcf5e8ddg_india-x-bcci_625x300_01_December_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwenty-one%20of%20the%2025%20most%20venomous%20snakes%20in%20the%20world%20can%20be%20found%20in%20Australia.%20But%20they%20are%20not%20the%20only%20deadly%20things%20Down%20Under.%20Just%20ask%20any%20visiting%20Test%20team.%20The%20pitches%2C%20the%20weather%2C%20the%20aggression%2C%20the%20crowd%2C%20the%20players%2C%20the%20overwhelming%20stadiums%2C%20the%20centuries-old%20history%20of%20Australian%20cricket%20that%20tells%20tales%20of%20unmatched%20glory%20and%20dominance%E2%80%94it's%20almost%20like%20it%20was%20all%20meticulously%20designed%20to%20make%20touring%20parties%20feel%20uncomfortable%20and%20eventually%20fold%20and%20surrender.%20Consider%20this%3Afrom%201993-94%20to%202008-09%2C%20the%20Aussies%20were%20unbeaten%20at%20home%20in%2028%20consecutive%20home%20Test%20series.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20last%20three%20decades%20(1994-95%20to%20now)%2C%20Australia%20have%20a%20Test%20win%20percentage%20of%20over%2080%20at%20home.%20Not%20surprisingly%2C%20tales%20of%20a%20Test%20match%20or%20series%20win%20by%20a%20visiting%20team%20are%20passed%20down%20from%20father%20to%20son%20to%20grandson.%20Jasprit%20Bumrah%20spoke%20about%20how%20he%20has%20%E2%80%98stories'%20to%20share%20with%20his%20son%20when%20he%20grows%20up%20after%20India%20won%20the%20Perth%20Test%20this%20time%20to%20go%201-0%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Growing%20Self-Confidence%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20then%2C%20not%20too%20many%20teams%20sport%20the%20badge%20of%20having%20beaten%20Australia%20in%20Australia.%20From%202000%20till%20now%2C%20only%20two%20teams%20have%20won%20consecutive%20Test%20series%20in%20Australia%E2%80%94South%20Africa%20(2008-16)%20and%20India%20(2018-19%20and%202020-21).%20And%20if%20the%20first%20Test%20of%20the%20ongoing%20series%20in%20Perth%20was%20anything%20to%20go%20by%2C%20it%20would%20be%20fair%20to%20say%20that%20Team%20India%20is%20a%20different%20beast%20altogether%20in%20Australian%20conditions%20now.%20No%20matter%20how%20wounded%20they%20are%2C%20no%20matter%20how%20young%20the%20squad%2C%20the%20self-belief%20that%20they%20can%20beat%20the%20Aussies%20in%20their%20own%20den%20is%20something%20that%20does%20not%20desert%20them%20these%20days.%20Though%20they%20had%20won%20historic%20back-to-back%20series%20on%20their%20last%20two%20tours%2C%20this%20time%2C%20Team%20India%20went%20into%20the%20five-Test%20series%20as%20the%20underdogs.%20After%20all%2C%20they%20had%20been%20whitewashed%20by%20the%20Kiwis%20and%20completely%20humbled%20at%20home%20in%20a%20three-Test%20series%20for%20the%20first%20time%20ever.%20That%20coupled%20with%20the%20fact%20that%20Australia%20began%20the%20series%20as%20the%20No.%201%20team%20and%20that%20the%20first%20Test%20was%20played%20at%20the%20traditionally%20fast%20and%20bouncy%20Western%20Australia%20venue%20of%20Perth%20(albeit%20at%20the%20newer%20Optus%20stadium)%20meant%20that%20the%20home%20team%20were%20tagged%20favourites.%20And%20yet%2C%20the%20ultimate%20result%20was%20a%20comprehensive%20295-run%20win%20for%20India%20as%20they%20breached%20the%20Perth%20fortress%E2%80%94something%20they%20couldn't%20do%20on%20their%202018-19%20tour%20(Perth%20didn't%20host%20a%20Test%20on%20India's%20last%20tour%20in%202020-21).%20And%20that%20too%20without%20the%20services%20of%20the%20likes%20of%20Rohit%20Sharma%2C%20Shubman%20Gill%20and%20Mohammed%20Shami.%20According%20to%20reports%20from%20Australia%2C%20India%20are%20the%20bookmakers'%20favourites%20to%20win%20the%20series%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVirat%20Kohli's%20one-line%20response%20after%20Australian%20Prime%20Minister%20Anthony%20Albanese%20complimented%20him%20and%20the%20Indian%20team%20for%20their%20performance%20in%20Perth%20this%20time%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe've%20always%20got%20to%20add%20our%20own%20spice%20to%20it%E2%80%9D%2C%20was%20reflective%20in%20many%20ways%20of%20the%20confidence%20that%20the%20Indian%20team%20exudes%20on%20Australian%20shores%20these%20days.%20Gone%20are%20the%20days%20when%20a%20draw%20was%20considered%20to%20be%20a%20suitable%20result.%20Now%2C%20it's%20all%20about%20the%20win%2C%20regardless%20of%20venue.%20There's%20not%20an%20iota%20of%20a%20fear%20factor.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat's%20Driving%20Team%20India%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndian%20teams%20of%20the%20past%20fought%20valiantly%20against%20the%20mighty%20Aussies%20on%20their%20shores%2C%20with%20many%20heroes%20emerging.%20Now%20they%20go%20in%20armed%20with%20the%20self-confidence%20that%20they%20are%20the%20better%20team.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20see%20the%20same%20confidence%20building%20up%20in%20the%20fans%20as%20well.%20Indian%20fans%20these%20days%20expect%20to%20see%20superlative%20performances%20from%20the%20travelling%20players.%20A%20series%20win%20in%20Australia%20is%20no%20longer%20the%20holy%20grail%20of%20foreign%20travel%20for%20the%20Indian%20team.%20It's%20sweet%2C%20but%20no%20longer%20surprising.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20what%20has%20changed%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20main%20ingredient%20in%20the%20recipe%20for%20success%20for%20Team%20India%20Down%20Under%20is%20self-belief%E2%80%94staunch%2C%20unwavering%20belief%20that%20they%20can%20tackle%20whatever%20is%20thrown%20their%20way%20and%20also%2C%20most%20importantly%2C%20give%20the%20Aussies%20a%20taste%20of%20their%20own%20medicine.%20The%20world%20saw%20how%20India%20bounced%20back%20after%20being%20bowled%20out%20for%20150%20in%20their%20first%20innings%20in%20the%20Perth%20Test%20to%20skittle%20out%20Australia%20for%20104%20in%20their%20first.%20On%20their%20last%20tour%2C%20they%20roared%20back%20after%20being%20bundled%20out%20for%2036%20in%20the%20first%20Test%E2%80%94their%20all-time%20lowest%20innings%20total%E2%80%94to%20ultimately%20win%20the%20series.%20They%20know%20they%20will%20be%20hit%2C%20but%20they%20also%20know%20that%20they%20can%20get%20right%20back%20up%20and%20deliver%20a%20counter-punch.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20Test%20team%20has%20been%20a%20real%20force%20to%20be%20reckoned%20with%20for%20decades%20now%2C%20but%20on%20the%20Aussie%20shores%2C%20the%20winds%20of%20change%20began%20to%20really%20blow%20from%20the%202014-15%20tour.%20India%20lost%20the%204%20Test%20series%200-2%2C%20but%20after%20losing%20the%20first%20two%20Tests%20in%20Adelaide%20and%20Brisbane%2C%20the%20way%20they%20held%20on%20for%20two%20straight%20draws%20in%20Melbourne%20and%20Sydney%20drew%20praise%20from%20all%20quarters.%20In%20fact%2C%20in%20Adelaide%2C%20chasing%20364%20for%20a%20win%2C%20they%20almost%20pulled%20off%20an%20improbable%20win%2C%20getting%20to%20315%20in%20their%20second%20innings.%20India%20lost%20the%20series%2C%20but%20the%20major%20takeaway%20was%20the%20belief%20that%20they%20were%20getting%20very%20close%20to%20vanquishing%20the%20mighty%20Aussies%20on%20their%20own%20soil.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EThe%20Last%20Two%20Tours%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20that%20knowledge%20is%20what%20the%20touring%20Indian%20party%20carried%20with%20them%20for%20the%202018-19%20and%202020-21%20tours.%20Both%20were%20four-Test%20series%20and%20India%20won%20both%20by%20a%20margin%20of%202-1.%20After%20becoming%20the%20first%20Asian%20team%20to%20win%20a%20Test%20series%20in%20Australia%20in%202018-19%2C%20on%20the%20last%20tour%2C%20the%20Indian%20batters%20put%20their%20bodies%20on%20the%20line%2C%20as%20injury%20after%20injury%20ravaged%20their%20camp.%20They%20had%20to%20rely%20on%20net%20bowlers%20to%20draw%20up%20a%20playing%20XI%2C%20and%20yet%2C%20while%20being%20down%20to%20265%2F5%2C%20chasing%20328%20to%20win%20in%20the%20last%20Test%20in%20Brisbane%20and%20without%20the%20services%20of%20Virat%2C%20they%20were%20confident%20enough%20to%20go%20for%20the%20win%20and%20not%20try%20and%20settle%20for%20a%20safe%20draw.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20series%20was%20locked%20at%201-1%20at%20that%20stage.%20They%20risked%20a%20series%20loss%20to%20pull%20off%20an%20unforgettable%203-wicket%20match%20win%20that%20also%20gave%20them%20the%20series.%20This%20win%2C%20while%20scripting%20Test%20cricket%20history%2C%20did%20two%20very%20important%20things%E2%80%94it%20was%20validation%20that%20offence%20could%20be%20the%20best%20form%20of%20defense%20in%20Australia%2C%20and%20it%20sent%20out%20a%20very%20strong%20message%20to%20the%20Aussie%20camp%20that%20their%20traditional%20fortresses%20were%20no%20longer%20safe.%20If%20you%20can%20dig%20your%20claws%20into%20your%20opposition's%20psyche%2C%20that%20mental%20hold%20can%20be%20very%20difficult%20to%20shake%20off.%20We%20all%20saw%20how%20the%20body%20language%20of%20the%20Australians%20almost%20suggested%20that%20they%20had%20given%20up%20when%20the%20Indian%20batters%20refused%20to%20give%20an%20inch%20in%20their%20second%20innings%20of%20the%20Perth%20Test%20this%20time%2C%20piling%20up%20487%2F6%20declared.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EYoung%20Blood%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIdentifying%20young%20talent%20who%20can%20be%20game%20changers%20and%20are%20ready%20to%20fight%20fire%20with%20fire%2C%20and%20throwing%20them%20into%20the%20deep%20end%20if%20required%2C%20has%20also%20been%20a%20strategy%20that's%20worked.%20While%20old%20warhorses%20like%20Cheteshwar%20Pujara%20and%20Ajinkya%20Rahane%20stood%20tall%2C%20some%20of%20the%20main%20architects%20of%20India's%20series%20win%2C%20especially%20the%20crucial%20fourth%20Test%20win%20on%20their%20last%20tour%2C%20were%20players%20like%20Shubman%20Gill%2C%20Rishabh%20Pant%2C%20Mohammed%20Siraj%2C%20Washington%20Sundar%2C%20Shardul%20Thakur%20and%20T.%20Natarajan.%20Pant%20and%20Gill%20were%20the%20third%20and%20sixth-highest%20run-getters%2C%20respectively%2C%20on%20the%20tour.%20In%20Mohammed%20Siraj%2C%20the%20team%20realised%20that%20they%20had%20found%20a%20bowler%20who%20could%20take%20the%20rigours%20of%20Test%20cricket%20while%20troubling%20the%20best%20in%20the%20world.%20Siraj%20made%20his%20Test%20debut%20in%20the%20second%20Test%20in%20Melbourne%20on%20the%20last%20tour%20and%20finished%20as%20India's%20leading%20wicket-taker%20and%20the%20third-highest%20overall%20(13%20wickets).%20He%20lost%20his%20father%20while%20he%20was%20in%20Australia%2C%20during%20the%20Covid-19%20pandemic%2C%20but%20chose%20to%20stay%20on%20and%20play.%20Natarajan%20went%20from%20net%20bowler%20to%20making%20his%20debut%20across%20all%20three%20formats%20on%20that%20tour.%20On%20the%20current%20tour%2C%20the%20leading%20run%20scorer%20so%20far%20(before%20the%20start%20of%20the%20second%20Test)%20is%20the%2022-year-old%20Yashasvi%20Jaiswal%20(161%20runs)%E2%80%94only%20the%20third%20Indian%20cricketer%20to%20score%20a%20century%20on%20his%20debut%20tour%20of%20Australia.%20Harshit%20Rana's%20selection%20raised%20a%20few%20eyebrows.%20As%20things%20stand%20right%20now%2C%20the%2022-year-old%20from%20Delhi%20is%20the%20third-highest%20wicket-taker%20(4%20wickets)%20in%20the%20current%20series.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IPL%20has%20also%20made%20a%20contribution.%20Thanks%20to%20international%20players%20spending%20so%20much%20time%20with%20young%20Indian%20talent%2C%20gone%20are%20the%20days%20when%20established%20international%20cricketers%20were%20put%20on%20a%20pedestal%20by%20their%20juniors.%20While%20there%20is%20a%20lot%20of%20respect%20for%20battle-hardened%20veterans%2C%20the%20young%20crop%20also%20believes%20that%20they%20are%20not%20inferior%20in%20any%20way.%20A%20Jaiswal%20will%20hit%20a%20Mitchell%20Starc%20or%20a%20Josh%20Hazelwood%20for%20a%20boundary%20off%20the%20first%20ball%20he%20faces.%20A%20Rana%20will%20not%20think%20twice%20before%20walking%20up%20to%20a%20batter%20on%20his%20follow-through%20to%20chirp%20in%20his%20ear%20a%20bit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EPitch%2C%20Perfect%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFast%20bowlers%20who%20have%20been%20coming%20up%20the%20ranks%20in%20recent%20times%20will%20also%20thank%20the%20changing%20nature%20of%20pitches%20used%20for%20domestic%20matches%20in%20India.%20Grass%20on%20Indian%20tracks%20is%20no%20longer%20an%20alien%20sighting.%20Earlier%20this%20year%2C%20the%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20Cricket%20Association%20became%20the%20first%20cricketing%20body%20in%20the%20country%20to%20install%20hybrid%20pitches%20at%20the%20Dharamsala%20stadium.%20These%20are%20natural%20turfs%20injected%20with%20synthetic%20fibres%20that%20allow%20the%20grass%20to%20regenerate%2C%20in%20turn%20allowing%20much%20more%20cricket%20to%20be%20played%20on%20a%20single%20surface.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new-age%20Indian%20batter%20is%20not%20afraid%20of%20going%20after%20the%20Aussie%20pacers%20and%20the%20fast-bowling%20set-up%20(fuelled%20by%20a%20now%20constant%20supply%20line)%20can%20rattle%20any%20opposition%20line-up%2C%20in%20any%20conditions.%3Cbr%3E%5CnRavi%20Shastri%20has%20backed%20the%20possibility%20of%20a%20hat-trick%20of%20series%20wins%20in%20Australia%20for%20India.%20As%20things%20stand%20right%20now%2C%20with%20Virat%20Kohli%20having%20found%20form%2C%20Rohit%20Sharma%20and%20Shubman%20poised%20to%20return%20to%20the%20playing%20XI%20and%20a%20possibility%20of%20Shami%20being%20added%20to%20the%20squad%20at%20a%20later%20date%2C%20you%20would%20have%20to%20be%20very%20brave%20to%20bet%20against%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(The%20author%20is%20a%20former%20sports%20editor%20and%20primetime%20sports%20news%20anchor.%20He%20is%20currently%20a%20columnist%2C%20features%20writer%20and%20stage%20actor)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733304420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fcf5e8ddg_india-x-bcci_625x300_01_December_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fcricket-taming-the-aussies-how-india-is-staying-on-top-down-under-7169819%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Indian%20teams%20of%20the%20past%20fought%20valiantly%20against%20the%20mighty%20Aussies%20on%20their%20shores%2C%20with%20many%20heroes%20emerging.%20Now%20they%20go%20in%20armed%20with%20the%20self-confidence%20that%20they%20are%20the%20better%20team.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fcricket-taming-the-aussies-how-india-is-staying-on-top-down-under-7169819%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Countdown%20For%20ISRO's%20PSLV%20Rocket%20Continues%3A%20No%20Threat%20From%20Cyclone%20Fengal%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20massive%20Cyclone%20Fengal%2C%20which%20struck%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20coast%20along%20the%20Bay%20of%20Bengal%20earlier%20this%20week%2C%20has%20not%20dampened%20the%20countdown%20for%20ISRO's%20workhorse%20rocket%2C%20set%20to%20lift%20off%20in%20a%20few%20hours.%20Experts%20from%20ISRO%20stationed%20at%20the%20Satish%20Dhawan%20Space%20Centre%20confirmed%20to%20NDTV%20that%20the%20%26quot%3Bcountdown%20is%20progressing%20normally%2C%20and%20the%20weather%20is%20favourable%20for%20a%20nominal%20lift-off%20at%204%3A08%20pm.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20rocket%20port%2C%20located%20on%20Sriharikota%20Island%20along%20the%20Bay%20of%20Bengal%2C%20escaped%20the%20cyclone's%20fury%20as%20the%20storm%20made%20landfall%20farther%20south.%20On%20several%20occasions%2C%20rocket%20launches%20have%20been%20postponed%20due%20to%20cyclonic%20activity%2C%20but%20this%20time%20conditions%20remain%20optimal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%2061st%20flight%2C%20India's%20workhorse%20rocket%2C%20the%20Polar%20Satellite%20Launch%20Vehicle%20(PSLV)%2C%20has%20been%20tasked%20by%20the%20European%20Space%20Agency%20(ESA)%20to%20launch%20a%20unique%20pair%20of%20satellites%20designed%20to%20simulate%20a%20total%20solar%20eclipse%20through%20precision%20formation%20flying%20in%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20satellites%2C%20Proba-3%2C%20will%20lift%20off%20from%20Andhra%20Pradesh's%20Sriharikota%20on%20Wednesday%20at%204%3A08%20pm%20aboard%20the%20PSLV-C59.%20ISRO%20stated%20that%20the%20vehicle%20will%20place%20the%20Proba-3%20spacecraft%20into%20a%20highly%20elliptical%20orbit%20as%20part%20of%20a%20dedicated%20commercial%20mission%20under%20New%20Space%20India%20Limited%20(NSIL)%2C%20ISRO's%20commercial%20arm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fik71qasg_proba-3-_625x300_04_December_24.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProba-3%20is%20an%20in-orbit%20demonstration%20(IOD)%20mission%20by%20the%20ESA%2C%20aiming%20to%20showcase%20advanced%20formation-flying%20technologies.%20It%20consists%20of%20two%20spacecraft%3A%20the%20Coronagraph%20Spacecraft%20(CSC)%20and%20the%20Occulter%20Spacecraft%20(OSC).%20These%20will%20be%20launched%20together%20in%20a%20stacked%20configuration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWeighing%20a%20combined%20545%20kg%2C%20the%20two%20satellites%20will%20be%20carried%20into%20space%20by%20the%2044.5-meter-tall%20PSLV%20rocket%2C%20which%20weighs%20320%20tonnes%20at%20lift-off.%20Approximately%2018%20minutes%20after%20launch%2C%20the%20satellites%20will%20be%20deployed%20at%20an%20altitude%20of%20600%20km%20above%20Earth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Proba-3%20mission%20involves%20two%20mini-satellites%20flying%20in%20close%20formation%20with%20the%20ability%20to%20precisely%20control%20their%20attitude%20and%20separation.%20This%20innovative%20configuration%20simulates%20a%20total%20solar%20eclipse%20and%20demonstrates%20cutting-edge%20formation-flying%20and%20rendezvous%20technologies.%20According%20to%20ISRO%2C%20Proba-3%20is%20ESA's-and%20the%20world's-first%20precision%20formation-flying%20mission.%20The%20satellites%20will%20maintain%20a%20fixed%20configuration%20as%20if%20they%20were%20a%20single%20rigid%20structure%20in%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20marks%20the%20second%20ESA%20satellite%20launch%20aboard%20an%20Indian%20rocket.%20The%20first%2C%20the%20Proba-1%20mission%2C%20was%20launched%20in%202001%20using%20the%20PSLV.%20Originally%20planned%20as%20a%20one-year%20mission%2C%20Proba-1%20has%20exceeded%20expectations%2C%20remaining%20operational%20for%20over%20two%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733303880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2F8pvq33b8_proba-3-_625x300_04_December_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fisro-pslv-countdown-for-isros-pslv-rocket-continues-no-threat-from-cyclone-fengal-7169788%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20massive%20Cyclone%20Fengal%2C%20which%20struck%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20coast%20along%20the%20Bay%20of%20Bengal%20earlier%20this%20week%2C%20has%20not%20dampened%20the%20countdown%20for%20ISRO's%20workhorse%20rocket%2C%20set%20to%20lift%20off%20in%20a%20few%20hours.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fisro-pslv-countdown-for-isros-pslv-rocket-continues-no-threat-from-cyclone-fengal-7169788%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Suzlon%20Group%20secures%20order%20of%20302%20MW%20wind%20project%20from%20Jindal%20Renewables%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733303583000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fsuzlon-group-secures-order-of-302-mw-wind-project-from-jindal-renewables-124120400529_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20power%20generated%20will%20be%20used%20at%20steel%20plants%20in%20Chhattisgarh%20and%20Odisha%2C%20Suzlon%20said%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20Vietnamese%20Business%20Tycoon%20Masterminded%20World's%20Biggest%20Bank%20Fraud%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fproperty-tycoon-faces-death-penalty-over-biggest-fraud-in-vietnam-5417298%5C%22%3ETruong%20My%20Lan%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%2068-year-old%20influential%20Vietnamese%20property%20magnate%2C%20has%20lost%20the%20appeal%20against%20her%20death%20sentence%20for%20orchestrating%20the%20world's%20largest%20bank%20fraud.%20The%2068-year-old%20has%20been%20battling%20to%20avoid%20execution.%20Vietnam%20law%20stipulated%20repaying%2075%20per%20cent%C2%A0of%20the%20stolen%20amount%20could%20reduce%20her%20sentence%20to%20life%20imprisonment.%20Despite%20her%20recent%20plea%20for%20leniency%2C%20Lan%20is%20racing%20against%20time%20to%20repay%20%249%20billion%2C%20three-quarters%20of%20the%20%2412%20billion%20she%20was%20found%20to%20have%20embezzled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhere%20it%20all%20began%20for%20Truong%20My%20Lan%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETruong%20My%20Lan's%20journey%20from%20a%20market%20vendor%20to%20one%20of%20Vietnam's%20most%20powerful%20figures%20began%20in%20Ho%20Chi%20Minh%20City%2C%20where%20she%20sold%20cosmetics%20with%20her%20mother%2C%20as%20per%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%2Cnoindex%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcd753r47815o%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20BBC%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Capitalising%20on%20the%20economic%20reforms%20of%201986%2C%20she%20expanded%20her%20business%2C%20amassing%20a%20substantial%20property%20portfolio%20that%20included%20hotels%20and%20restaurants%20by%20the%201990s.%20By%20the%20time%20she%20became%20the%20chairwoman%20of%20Van%20Thinh%20Phat%20Group%2C%20her%20real%20estate%20empire%20was%20vast%2C%20and%20she%20had%20significant%20influence%20in%20the%20sector.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20fraud%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETruong%20My%20Lan's%20fraudulent%20activities%20were%20exposed%20following%20her%20arrest%20in%20October%202022.%20Prosecutors%20revealed%20she%20secretly%20controlled%20Saigon%20Commercial%20Bank%20(SCB)%2C%20the%20country's%20fifth-largest%20lender.%20Between%202012%20and%202022%2C%20Lan%20used%20numerous%20shell%20companies%20and%20third%20parties%20to%20orchestrate%20a%20vast%20financial%20scheme%20involving%20fake%20loan%20applications.%20This%20scheme%20allowed%20her%20to%20siphon%20off%20an%20estimated%20%2412.5%20billion.%20Prosecutors%20estimated%20that%20the%20total%20damages%20from%20the%20fraud%20could%20have%20reached%20US%2427%20billion%2C%20which%2C%20in%202022%2C%20represented%20nearly%203%25%20of%20Vietnam's%20GDP.%20This%20fraud%20left%20thousands%20of%20ordinary%20citizens%20without%20their%20life%20savings%2C%20tied%20up%20in%20the%20bank%20and%20their%20real%20estate%20ventures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20mask%20the%20fraud%2C%20Lan%20and%20her%20co-conspirators%2C%20including%20former%20bank%20executives%20and%20government%20officials%2C%20allegedly%20paid%20bribes%20of%20%245.2%20million%20to%20state%20officials%20%E2%80%94%20an%20amount%20that%20was%20the%20largest%20recorded%20bribe%20in%20Vietnam's%20history.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3EThe%20trial%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20trial%20involved%2085%20defendants%2C%20including%20Lan's%20husband%2C%20a%20Hong%20Kong%20businessman%2C%20and%20her%20niece.%20The%20authorities%20had%20to%20secure%20105%20boxes%20of%20evidence%2C%20weighing%20over%20six%20tonnes%2C%20and%20installed%20security%20cameras%20to%20safeguard%20the%20information.%20In%20April%202024%2C%2