and%20green%20spaces.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETackling%20roadblocks%20and%20achieving%20success%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Praveen%E2%80%99s%20work%20has%20taken%20him%20across%20the%20rural%20and%20tribal%20areas%20of%20Chittoor%2C%20Kurnool%2C%20and%20Nellore%2C%20where%20healthcare%20infrastructure%20is%20either%20rudimentary%20or%20non-existent.%20The%20lack%20of%20resources%20has%20never%20deterred%20him%2C%20instead%2C%20it%20has%20spurred%20him%20to%20innovate.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20to%20be%20resourceful%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20these%20villages%2C%20we%20may%20not%20have%20fancy%20equipment%2C%20but%20we%20have%20our%20hands%2C%20our%20knowledge%2C%20and%20the%20willingness%20to%20help.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20rural%20communities%2C%20Dr%20Praveen%20treats%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20ailments%2C%20from%20simple%20infections%20to%20complex%20chronic%20diseases.%20He%20also%20leads%20public%20health%20initiatives%20to%20improve%20overall%20health%20outcomes.%20His%20work%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F289418%2Fhealth-benefits-of-jackfruit-seeds-for-anaemia-boosting-immunity-science%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eanaemia%20prevention%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20in%20particular%2C%20has%20saved%20countless%20lives.%20One%20patient%2C%20Sarojama%20(40)%2C%20from%20Battamdoddi%20village%2C%20recalls%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20struggling%20with%20my%20health%20for%20over%20a%20year.%20No%20one%20knew%20what%20was%20wrong.%20Dr%20Praveen%20visited%20our%20village%20once%20and%20diagnosed%20me%20with%20anaemia.%20I%20followed%20his%20treatment%2C%20and%20within%20a%20few%20weeks%2C%20I%20began%20to%20recover.%20My%20haemoglobin%20level%20was%20initially%20around%20eight%2C%20but%20thanks%20to%20his%20care%2C%20it%20has%20now%20ris